snippet.title: Flip Out Rush - Update 1.5 (Love & Stickers!) Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Love is in the air in Flip Out Rush!

Update 1.5 is packed with a brand new Event: "Heartbeat Derby," A New Achievement system with a ton of stickers to unlock, and a new tier of vaults to unlock!

New Unlockables, Bug Fixes, and Quality of Life improvements await you in Flip Out Rush Update 1.5! Available Now!

Read more about Flip Out Rush Update 1.5 here!: https://grimkittyproductions.wixsite.com/home/post/flip-out-rush-update-1-5-changelog-patch-notes

Download the game today!: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.grimkitty.flipoutrush&pli=1

Song: EuGenius - TRAVEL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PIgSiVRlzBk
